metadata.name: Inverted Champagne SuperNova Fountain
metadata.description: The flights of fancy of the Digital Butler lead to a rabbit hole of the Uncanny. An inverted fountain of champagne made of Art Brut is manifested before your eyes. Champagne for My real friends and Real pain for my Sham friends-Bacon said it best. A near choke is spoke, for clearly Nobody is no Houdini! -thusly is the Spin.  Made in Brooklyn for the Upside Down World solo show exhibition by David Nobody
